    <bodyBottom>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>QMU Student President and QMU Court Member, Jay Brown, explains what GIVE could offer you:</p>
<div class="mceNonEditable embeditem" data-embed-url="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aIcwz62pMpk" data-embed-height="442" data-embed-width="920" data-embed-constrain="true"><iframe width="786" height="442" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/aIcwz62pMpk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen="" title="Jay Footage Part 1"></iframe></div>
<p> </p>
<p>QMU Student President and QMU Court Member, Jay Brown, explains why GIVE is important:</p>
<div class="mceNonEditable embeditem" data-embed-url="https://youtu.be/vyiGarHokMk" data-embed-height="442" data-embed-width="920" data-embed-constrain="true"><iframe width="786" height="442" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/vyiGarHokMk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen="" title="Jay Part 2"></iframe></div>]]></Value>
